---
// Public Key Certificate / digital signature flow with a Certifying Authority.
---
<figure class="figure">
  <svg viewBox="0 0 440 230" role="img" aria-label="Sender signs with a private key; receiver verifies with the public key vouched for by a Certifying Authority">
    <!-- CA on top -->
    <rect x="160" y="14" width="120" height="38" rx="8" class="dgm-fill-accent"></rect>
    <text x="220" y="32" text-anchor="middle" class="dgm-inv" font-size="12" font-weight="700">Certifying Authority</text>
    <text x="220" y="46" text-anchor="middle" class="dgm-inv" font-size="10">issues the certificate</text>

    <!-- sender -->
    <rect x="20" y="120" width="120" height="56" rx="10" class="dgm-fill-surface dgm-stroke" stroke-width="1.5"></rect>
    <text x="80" y="142" text-anchor="middle" class="dgm-text" font-size="12" font-weight="600">Sender</text>
    <text x="80" y="160" text-anchor="middle" class="dgm-muted" font-size="10.5">signs with</text>
    <text x="80" y="172" text-anchor="middle" class="dgm-muted" font-size="10.5" font-weight="600">🔒 private key</text>

    <!-- receiver -->
    <rect x="300" y="120" width="120" height="56" rx="10" class="dgm-fill-surface dgm-stroke" stroke-width="1.5"></rect>
    <text x="360" y="142" text-anchor="middle" class="dgm-text" font-size="12" font-weight="600">Receiver</text>
    <text x="360" y="160" text-anchor="middle" class="dgm-muted" font-size="10.5">verifies with</text>
    <text x="360" y="172" text-anchor="middle" class="dgm-muted" font-size="10.5" font-weight="600">🔑 public key</text>

    <!-- signed message flow -->
    <line x1="140" y1="148" x2="300" y2="148" class="dgm-stroke-accent" stroke-width="2.5" marker-end="url(#arrowK)"></line>
    <text x="220" y="140" text-anchor="middle" class="dgm-muted" font-size="10.5">signed document</text>

    <!-- CA vouches lines -->
    <line x1="160" y1="44" x2="95" y2="118" class="dgm-stroke" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-dasharray="3 3"></line>
    <line x1="280" y1="44" x2="345" y2="118" class="dgm-stroke" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-dasharray="3 3" marker-end="url(#arrowK)"></line>
    <text x="318" y="86" text-anchor="middle" class="dgm-muted" font-size="9.5">"this key is</text>
    <text x="318" y="97" text-anchor="middle" class="dgm-muted" font-size="9.5">genuine"</text>

    <text x="220" y="206" text-anchor="middle" class="dgm-muted" font-size="11">A valid signature = authentic + unaltered (same legal weight as a handwritten one)</text>

    <defs>
      <marker id="arrowK" markerWidth="8" markerHeight="8" refX="6" refY="3" orient="auto">
        <path d="M0 0 L6 3 L0 6 z" class="dgm-fill-accent"></path>
      </marker>
    </defs>
  </svg>
  <figcaption>Asymmetric keys + a trusted Certifying Authority: the private key signs, the public key (vouched for by the certificate) verifies.</figcaption>
</figure>
